{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0018","text":"陪着你 陪着我 用冷飯暖胃","structure":{"line_index":18,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["陪伴","溫暖","愛"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["陪","冷飯","暖胃"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,0,2,5,2,5,2,5,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["pui4","zoek6","nei5","pui4","zoek6","ngo5","jung6","laang5","faan6","nyun5","wai6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"陪","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"陪","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"冷飯","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"暖","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"胃","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「陪着你 陪着我」強調互相陪伴，即使是「冷飯」也能「暖胃」，象徵著簡單的陪伴也能帶來溫暖與滿足。"},"source":{"title":"兩小無猜","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1939","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0017","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0019","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0019","text":"小小戀曲都驚世 偏心你改寫慣例","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛","獨特","偏愛"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["戀曲","驚世","偏心","改寫"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,9,3,3,3,4,3,3,5,9,9,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["siu2","siu2","lyun2","kuk1","dou1","geng1","sai3","pin1","sam1","nei5","goi2","se2","gwaan3","lai6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"小小","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"戀曲","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"驚世","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"偏心","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"改寫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"慣例","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「小小戀曲都驚世」誇張地形容愛情的獨特與重要，而「偏心你改寫慣例」則表達了對對方的特殊情感與為其改變的意願。"},"source":{"title":"兩小無猜","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1939","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0020","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0020","text":"愚鈍到 迷亂到 樂意讓青春荒廢","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["愛","犧牲","青春"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["愚鈍","迷亂","樂意","荒廢"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,0,2,4,2,4,2,3,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","deon6","dou3","mai4","lyun6","dou3","lok6","ji3","joeng6","cing1","ceon1","fong1","fai3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"愚鈍","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"到","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"迷亂","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"到","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"樂意","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"讓","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"青春","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"荒廢","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「愚鈍到 迷亂到」形容為愛而失去理智的狀態，但卻「樂意讓青春荒廢」，表達了為愛不計代價的投入。"},"source":{"title":"兩小無猜","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1939","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0021","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0021","text":"小小空間都珍貴 天空海闊不足以代替","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["愛","獨特","珍貴"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["空間","珍貴","代替"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,3,3,3,4,3,3,9,4,3,3,5,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["siu2","siu2","hung1","dou1","zan1","gwai3","tin1","hung1","hoi2","fut3","bat1","zuk1","ji5","doi6","tai3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"小小","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"空間","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"珍貴","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"天空海闊","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不足以","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"代替","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「小小空間都珍貴」強調兩人相處的點滴時光都極其寶貴，「天空海闊不足以代替」更是突顯了這份感情的無可取代性。"},"source":{"title":"兩小無猜","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1939","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTkzOQ_0020","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
